//Bursitis - Only one Localization selected

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 08 - Soft parts of Knee MRI
When I select the radio button 'Finding'
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Bursitis' from the Finding dropdown
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Bursa suprapatellaris' checkbox is enabled
And 'Bursa subcutanea praepatellaris' checkbox is enabled
And 'Bursa subfascialis praepatellaris' checkbox is enabled
And 'Bursa infrapatellaris profunda' checkbox is enabled

And 'Bursa anserina' checkbox is enabled
And 'Bursa within the inner band' checkbox is enabled
And 'Bursa subtendinea musculi semimembranosi' checkbox is enabled

And 'Bursa tractus iliotibialis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Bursa subtendinea musculi bicipitis femoris inferior' checkbox is enabled

When I select one of the above checkboxes
Then 'Ill-defined margins' radio button is enabled
And 'Circumscribed' radio button is enabled
And 'Max. diameter' input field is enabled
And 'Haemorrhage' checkbox is enabled